# ── Tshirt Designer — environment template ──────────────────────────────
# Copy to `.env` and fill in. Nothing here is required to run Part 1 (Foundation).
# Client-exposed values MUST be prefixed with VITE_. Secrets (keys) belong only
# in serverless functions — never expose them to the browser (ARCHITECTURE §8).

# Supabase (added in Part 4)
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# Razorpay (added in Part 5) — public key id only on the client
# VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=

# Server-only secrets (serverless functions, Parts 5–6) — DO NOT prefix with VITE_
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=
# POD_API_KEY=
